Hi everyone, I\'92m Lena Groeger, a developer/designer/journalist at ProPublica. Last year I worked with my colleagues Michael Grabell and Howard Berkes of NPR on a project about insurance. It sounds boring, but it turned into one of our most popular data visualizations ever. \
