I\'92m going to tell you about 5 things I learned in the process.\
\
The investigation was about workers compensation. In the US, workers get money if are injured on the job, but the agreement between labor and industry that has been slowly dismantled in the last few decades. Today for thousands of workers, a serious injury can lead to total disaster, which we wrote a big long story about.\
\
