\b 4. Take advantage of different forms.\

\b0 \
We ended up telling this story a number of ways. To show how states compared to each other, we used a small multiples comparison across all states. But to show how a specific state compared to the average, we let you click to see a side-by-side comparison.\
\
We also made an animated gif for to share on social media.\
